===Etymology===
; "to shoot pellets at; to play (a stringed instrument)"
: Probably related to {{inh|zh|tbq-pro|*tal||bow}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).
: Pronunciation 2 ("bow for shooting pellets" > "pellet") is a general derivation of pronunciation 1 "to shoot pellets at".
: See also {{och-l|憚|to fear}}, to which it has been alternatively linked with.

